# Plans

## Plan mode: REQUIRED post-creation step

After creating a plan with the CreatePlan tool, you MUST complete these steps before ending your turn:

1. Check whether the plan file exists in the **workspace** at `.cursor/plans/<name>.plan.md`.
2. If it was saved to the Cursor-level directory (`~/.cursor/plans/`) instead, copy it into the workspace at `.cursor/plans/` so it can be committed to the repo.
3. Confirm the file is in the workspace. Do not consider the plan complete until this is verified.
